Tzi Ma https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tzi_Ma 0 Tzi Ma (Chinese: 馬泰; born June 10, 1962) is a Hong Kong American character actor who has made numerous appearances in American films and television series including Dante's Peak, Rush Hour, 24, Arrival and The Man in the High Castle.
